2. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the car is the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the british is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person playing poker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Game           | billiard    | poker  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance       | mystery    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | rock       |
| Nationality   | russian       | british    |
